{"tid":305832,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去日本旅行識左個好特別既日本仔","createTime":"2017-07-02T04:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T14:38:02.000Z","uid":122968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a12b38f7cd873b7941778a3106111345e0eab6c1","tid":305832,"uid":122968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"前排去日本旅行住hostel識左個日本仔好friendly同幾多野講 <br />\n點知佢話自己好鐘意中國 成日去大陸旅行 仲癲到走去學普通話 同佢msg佢仲識打殘體字 最痴線係佢連Fb Ig icon都係 長城or上海既相 跟住我問佢點解 佢話覺得中國人好warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而日本人好冷漠<br />\n點解好似同香港人既諗法完全相反既"},{"pid":"f31e13703e40cefed0ec7da0d8fb4e9da09efd6a","tid":305832,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"可能食到好多女呢"},{"pid":"832c76ded2ce6ea70029f0487fea24020bc99213","tid":305832,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"中國人口裡說不 其實心底祟日囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad217e6f4f0fb1f2e6c1f1ddae9a9a836b9514c","tid":305832,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:01:30.000Z","msg":"佢對中國認識太少"},{"pid":"28be4b849d5992e35d3dede4424ad7135ce388e3","tid":305832,"uid":122968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢對中國認識太少</blockquote><br />\n其實唔少 佢曾經exchange 過去一年"},{"pid":"edde16d2030ed82176de0f01ac0bb2751e39691b","tid":305832,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:06:54.000Z","msg":"日本人係好冷漠wor"},{"pid":"fbaf4992127cfc11301e3dd741869b1b0f102b7d","tid":305832,"uid":10183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"每個地方都有崇x撚，不過一般都係崇鬼多，崇中都有，係小見咁解"},{"pid":"f9ce167d105d9ef4c1b369d26539d45a374ab930","tid":305832,"uid":122968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本人係好冷漠wor</blockquote><br />\n做朋友就好冷漠囉 對客人就好熱情 都唔知好定壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eb2a58f0af9b3ede89f927106e3ab56500d6d4","tid":305832,"uid":53880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"住同玩兩回事<br />\n佢應該唔會長住中國 用遊客角度睇野點都好既"},{"pid":"3a2320db221165bdbe3ee4fc544dc8d56db52af2","tid":305832,"uid":50980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"其實地道北京人真係好好人好熱情   我去過一個月實習個啲大媽當我係仔咁又請食野  又介紹我去邊玩  佢地做野又唔會好似香港咁趕  多好多時間吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:反共"},{"pid":"d5582dcde4e499c934078977fa99b33d7b9d5307","tid":305832,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4af4ac8de9fc15d53bd8a4d957a4a1c2eca91098","tid":305832,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實地道北京人真係好好人好熱情   我去過一個月實習個啲大媽當我係仔咁又請食野  又介紹我去邊玩  佢地做野又唔會好似香港咁趕  多好多時間吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:反共</blockquote><br />\n其實每個地方都有好人壞人"},{"pid":"f7ae2a6fdd693a28d853c2eb22875bf1d05be809","tid":305832,"uid":122968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旅行同生活係兩回事<br />\n你住hostel既話識既全部都係出黎玩既後生仔<br />\n基本上都好nice</blockquote><br />\n問題係佢身為日本人但好崇中好奇怪"},{"pid":"37ec9d5ebb27474a2e13675f859c697b2add3ae8","tid":305832,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似港女對鬼佬都好熱情"},{"pid":"b938a458f0355e05e5e37875049910f4ab261106","tid":305832,"uid":101231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"我去過二次北京玩 發覺北京人